---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Profile</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    Work in progress ...
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Education</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container grid gap-4 mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Computer Science and Engineering"
      subtitle="Erasmus Programme, University of Oslo, Oslo, Norway"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Science"
      subtitle="Master Degree, University of Verona, Verona, Italy"
    />
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Banking and Finance"
      subtitle="Bachelor of Arts, Brescia, Italy"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Experience</div>
  </div>

  <div class="time-line-container mb-10">
    <TimeLineElement
      title="AI Researcher"
      subtitle="Current at Equmenopolis - Tokyo, Japan"
    >
      Developed SynapseLink, a real-time audio-driven facial animation system generating 52 blendshapes at 25 fps (204× faster than real-time, single GPU). Designed a custom training objective for expressiveness (+91.8% over baseline), achieving a 43× lighter model than FaceFormer/CodeTalker. Optimized the production pipeline with tensor caching (57× speedup), mixed-precision training, and streaming inference. Unity & Unreal ready via ARKit.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="2025-2026 EU Vulcanus in Japan Fellow"
      subtitle="EU-Japan Centre for Industrial Cooperation - Tokyo, Japan"
    >
      https://www.eu-japan.eu/
      
      For 2025-2026 edition, among 500+ candidates with STEM degrees from all EU, selected as 1 of 23 participants for the industrial internship program "Vulcanus in Japan" (initiative co-funded by the European Commission and the Japanese METI).
      
      About the EU-Japan Centre: the Centre is co-funded by the European Commission and the Japanese Ministry of Economy, Trade & Industry. It manages managerial training courses, seminars, researches, student internships and other services all designed to help bring EU and Japanese businesses together. The EU-Japan Centre is member of Enterprise Europe Network.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Data Scientist"
      subtitle="at HPA, Math to Innovate - Trento, Italy"
    >
      Designed and shipped a suite of AI-native tools for autonomous agents: a privacy-preserving search layer (custom SearXNG backend, now core in several RAG pipelines), an AI-Agent / DB-Agent architecture for low-latency grounded retrieval, and LLM-powered automation pipelines that replaced manual multi-step operations. Owned the full path to production (observability, testing, fallbacks) and led enablement sessions to scale adoption across teams.
    </TimeLineElement>
    <TimeLineElement
      title="Intern as Machine Learning Engineer"
      subtitle="at HPA, Math to Innovate - Trento, Italy"
    >
      Built BonsaiParser, a modular document parsing framework with smart image filtering and enrichment optimized for RAG pipelines. Fine-tuned WASTE, a computer vision model for waste recognition, applying advanced image processing to improve detection accuracy. Designed a multi-agent system to orchestrate and optimize feature extraction in RAG workflows, improving contextual retrieval quality.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Certifications</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2">
    <li>
      2025-2026 EU Vulcanus in Japan Fellowship (one of 23 selected across Europe from 500+ applicants)
    </li>
      <li>
      Check
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/gabrieledurante/" target="_blank">  LinkedIn</a> for full list of certifications
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Skills</div>
  </div>

  <ul class="list-disc md:columns-5 columns-2 mx-6">
    <li>NLP</li>
    <li>LLMs</li>
    <li>Python</li>
    <li>PyTorch</li>
    <li>TensorFlow</li>
    <li>Deep Learning</li>
    <li>Dialog Systems</li>
    <li>Instruction Tuning</li>
    <li>SQL</li>
    <li>Leadership</li>
    <li>Public Speaking</li>
    <li>Social Impact</li>
    <li>Italian (Native)</li>
    <li>English (Fluent)</li>
    <li>Japanese (Basic)</li>
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
